OL,3,CHow virtual reality could help teens
OL,4,Cgrasp the dangers of carrying a knife
OL,6,FA virtual reality experience which
OL,7,Fconfronts young people with the
OL,8,Fpotentially deadly consequences of
OL,9,Fcarrying a knife could be used to
OL,10,Ftackle the issue.
OL,12,FThe interactive film gives people the
OL,13,Fchance to explore a situation using a
OL,14,Fvirtual reality (VR) headset, making
OL,15,Fdecisions which have varying
OL,16,Fconsequences.
