OL,3,CHow virtual reality could help teens
OL,4,Cgrasp the dangers of carrying a knife
OL,6,FShadow home secretary Yvette Cooper
OL,7,Ftook part in the experience at the
OL,8,Flatest meeting of the North East
OL,9,FTaskforce, a forum organised by The
OL,10,FNorthern Echo newspaper.
OL,12,FDescribing the VR experience as
OL,13,F"powerful", she said: "It's real. It's
OL,14,Flike you're there, sitting in the park
OL,15,Fwith these teenagers, talking to them
OL,16,Fabout what's happening and what
OL,17,Fthey're worrying about.
