OL,3,CHow virtual reality could help teens
OL,4,Cgrasp the dangers of carrying a knife
OL,6,FShe added: "It's used in a
OL,7,Fpreventative space, with young people
OL,8,Fnot involved in criminality.
OL,10,F"For them, it's about understanding
OL,11,Fwhat the possible consequences of
OL,12,Fcarrying a knife can be.
OL,14,F"We're not demonising every young
OL,15,Fperson saying every young person
OL,16,Fcarries a knife but it's about them
OL,17,Funderstanding the consequences of
OL,18,Factions and for them to feel it in an
OL,19,Femotive way."
