OL,3,CHow virtual reality could help teens
OL,4,Cgrasp the dangers of carrying a knife
OL,6,FThe task force brings together people
OL,7,Fincluding families who have lost loved
OL,8,Fones to knife crime, MPs, police and
OL,9,Fother agencies in the hope of reducing
OL,10,Fcrime rates.
OL,12,FAlison Madgin, whose 18-year-old
OL,13,Fdaughter Samantha was stabbed and
OL,14,Fkilled in 2007, is among those who has
OL,15,Fbeen taking part in the forum.
OL,17,F"It's very important," she said. "You
OL,18,Fcan't do it on your own. Everyone has
OL,19,Fto work together. It's the only way
OL,20,Fit's going to work."
