OL,3,CHow virtual reality could help teens
OL,4,Cgrasp the dangers of carrying a knife
OL,6,FShe added: "Until changes are made it
OL,7,Fwill stay the same, or get worse."
OL,9,FTanya and Simon Brown, from
OL,10,FSunderland, set up the following the
OL,11,Fkilling of their son in 2019.
OL,13,FSimon said: "The more voices we have
OL,14,Fas a collective, the louder we get and
OL,15,Fthe more people sit up and listen to
OL,16,Fthe point we're trying to make - it's
OL,17,Fnot ok to carry a knife or use a
OL,18,Fknife. It has to stop.
